📖 Explanation
🏫 Account = College

The organization providing services.

Example:

Engineering College
University
👨‍🎓 Contact = Student

The person connected to the organization.

Example:

Student applying for admission
📩 Lead = Interested Student

A student who:

asks about courses
visits website
requests admission details

but has not yet applied.

🎯 Opportunity = Admission Process

The active admission application that may result in successful enrollment.

Example:

Application review
Fee discussion
Seat confirmation
